    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-05-04T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-05-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="392"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d392">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">800.51W89 Finland/32</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Finnish Minister (<persName type="from">Åström</persName>)
                        to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-05-04">May 4,
                            1932</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: With reference to our conversation yesterday
                    relative to the third paragraph of the draft to an agreement for the
                    postponement of payments due, under the terms of the debt-funding agreement
                    between Finland and the United States of May 1, 1923, during the American fiscal
                    year beginning July 1, 1931 and ending June 30, 1932, I have the honor to inform
                    you that no Government of any foreign country is indebted to the Government of
                    Finland in respect of war, relief, or reparation debts.</p>
                <pb facs="0727" n="607" xml:id="pg_607"/>
                <p>I should highly appreciate it if you would be good enough to bring the above
                    information to the knowledge of the Secretary of the Treasury.</p>
                <p>Accept [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName>L. <hi rend="smallcaps">Åström</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
